256
00:09:42,669 --> 00:09:45,062
- Are you debt-free
and making six figures a year?

257
00:09:45,106 --> 00:09:46,977
- Uh, well--
- Then you're rich.

258
00:09:47,021 --> 00:09:48,762
- Yeah, but not, like,
rich-rich.

259
00:09:48,805 --> 00:09:51,242
- Are most of your friends
other doctors?

260
00:09:51,286 --> 00:09:52,287
- I mean, kind of, but--

261
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:53,505
- So then
your friends are rich.

262
00:09:53,549 --> 00:09:55,072
What are you getting at, Todd?

263
00:09:55,116 --> 00:09:56,639
- Well, actually,
you're a lot like the board.

264
00:09:56,683 --> 00:09:58,206
