269
00:10:03,167 --> 00:10:04,168
It's totally different.

270
00:10:04,212 --> 00:10:05,343
- Okay.
- You know what, Todd?

271
00:10:05,387 --> 00:10:06,606
You're dismissed.

272
00:10:11,045 --> 00:10:12,176
- Rohan Beta!

273
00:10:13,264 --> 00:10:14,439
