saphenous vein graft site,

465
00:17:19,342 --> 00:17:21,257
and the position
looks good to me.

466
00:17:21,301 --> 00:17:22,824
We're ready to proceed.

467
00:17:22,867 --> 00:17:24,304
- Okay.

468
00:17:24,347 --> 00:17:25,609
- Alicia, go ahead and start
the general anesthetic.

469
00:17:25,653 --> 00:17:28,090
And for you,
I've got some good news.

470
00:17:28,134 --> 00:17:32,877
- Usually you wait till
after the surgery to say that.

471
00:17:32,921 --> 00:17:35,228
- I was just appointed
to the hospital board.

472
00:17:35,271 --> 00:17:37,882
And for my first act in office,
I intend to make sure

473
00:17:37,926 --> 00:17:40,015
you have someone
to check on you post-op--

474
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:41,147
free of charge.

475
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:42,322
- You can do that?

476
00:17:42,365 --> 00:17:43,888
- Oh, absolutely.

477
00:17:43,932 --> 00:17:45,194
See you when you wake up.

478
00:17:46,152 --> 00:17:47,196
- Dr. Reynolds!

479
00:17:49,198 --> 00:17:51,244
- I'm in the middle
of something.

480
00:17:51,287 --> 00:17:52,854
- Okay,
I have some bad news,

481
00:17:52,897 --> 00:17:54,247
so I'm just gonna say it really
fast: you're not on the board.

482
00:17:54,290 --> 00:17:56,118
- What?
Well, who'd you get?

483
00:17:56,162 --> 00:17:57,293
- No one.

484
00:17:57,337 --> 00:17:58,990
They just, you know,
didn't want you.

485
00:18:00,122 --> 00:18:02,472
Max, I just promised this woman

486
00:18:02,516 --> 00:18:05,171
that we would look after her
this time around.

487
00:18:05,214 --> 00:18:06,433
- And we're gonna
keep that promise.

488
00:18:06,476 --> 00:18:08,174
- How, exactly?

489
00:18:08,217 --> 00:18:10,393
I think I know.

490
00:18:13,004 --> 00:18:14,571
- Do you know how hard
the FDA makes it

491
00:18:14,615 --> 00:18:16,530
to answer one simple question?

492
00:18:16,573 --> 00:18:17,879
- What's the question?

493
00:18:17,922 --> 00:18:19,533
- If we put this hip
into someone's body,

494
00:18:19,576 --> 00:18:20,882
will it kill them?

495
00:18:20,925 --> 00:18:22,449
- Is that a real question?

496
00:18:22,492 --> 00:18:24,973
- The FDA stopped approving
metal-on-metal hips in 2016

497
00:18:25,016 --> 00:18:26,540
