but how does that help

498
00:18:26,583 --> 00:18:30,283
the 3,000 patients that we gave
these hips to before 2016?

499
00:18:30,326 --> 00:18:31,458
- I am so glad you asked that,

500
00:18:31,501 --> 00:18:33,286
because that is
exactly the kind of issue

501
00:18:33,329 --> 00:18:34,548
that you are gonna be solving

502
00:18:34,591 --> 00:18:37,420
when you are on the board
of New Amsterdam.

503
00:18:37,464 --> 00:18:38,682
- On the board?

504
00:18:38,726 --> 00:18:40,293
You're my first choice.

505
00:18:40,336 --> 00:18:42,425
You don't want Dr. Sharpe,
you want Dr. Helen.

506
00:18:42,469 --> 00:18:44,427
- Yes, that is true,
